==Box office==
The film grossed HK$37,033,685 at the Hong Kong box office during its theatrical run from 29 January to 16 March 1994 in [[Hong Kong]].

==Award nominations==
*'''[[14th Hong Kong Film Awards]]'''
**Nominated: [[Hong Kong Film Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]] ([[Chow Yun-fat]])
**Nominated: [[Hong Kong Film Award for Best Cinematography|Best Cinematography]] ([[Peter Pau]])

